name: Vessels 180: Deep One Cultist
description:
Some of the colony’s citizens have a strange attraction to the strange alien race known as ‘The Deep Ones’.  Body modification tech allows them to do pretty much whatever they can image to themselves.  Things can get a little extreme.  This lady seems to have spliced octopus DNA with her own to achieve this look.  
She does look rather fetching we think you’ll agree ?
